headline: Azura Credit Union Modernizes Technology Infrastructure with Jack Henry
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) is pleased to announce that Azura Credit Union has selected Jack Henry's Symitar® open technology platform to deliver modern services to local communities and drive future growth.
